---
---
<div class="inverter-card">
  <div class="inverter-header">
    <iconify-icon icon="mdi:swap-vertical-bold"></iconify-icon>
    Cálculo Inverso: ¿Cuánto necesito repostar?
  </div>
  <div class="inverter-row">
    <div class="compact-group">
        <label for="inv-dist">Distancia Deseada</label>
        <div class="field-wrapper">
            <iconify-icon icon="mdi:map-marker-distance"></iconify-icon>
            <input type="number" id="inv-dist" class="compact-input" placeholder="Ej: 50" step="1" autocomplete="off" />
            <span class="unit-tag">MN</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="inverter-result">
        <span class="stat-label">Combustible Mínimo Requerido</span>
        <span class="inverter-value" id="inv-res">0 <small>L</small></span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-light); margin: 0; opacity: 0.8;">
    *Incluye el factor de reserva configurado anteriormente.
  </p>
</div>
